      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "CHANGE+- This form provides the same data as the DELTA form with the"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "addition of up to ten matching lines before and after each"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "differences section."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "LONG+- Lists the entire new file with all differences noted and a                                      ai"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "summary section. This is the most detailed level of reporting"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "available."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "OUTPUT"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "This specifies the report is to be sent."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "BROWSE+- The report is placed in a temporary file SUPERC.TMP and BROWSE"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "in invoked on that file. When you exit from BROWSE the temporary"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "file is deleted."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "PRINTER+- The report is sent to the current logical printer. See Print"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Setup Option 0.2 for details on selecting and setting up logical"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "printers."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
